-Aku juga. -Ya.

142
00:08:55.169 --> 00:08:56.269
Petugas Takagi.

143
00:08:56.269 --> 00:08:59.369
Bisakah kau menyelidiki kasus lainnya?

144
00:08:59.369 --> 00:09:00.969
Baik.

145
00:09:04.069 --> 00:09:07.869
Jika saja dia menyadari presiden sudah tewas...

146
00:09:07.869 --> 00:09:11.769
Dia takkan melakukan kejahatan itu.

147
00:09:12.969 --> 00:09:15.069
"Kantor Polisi Metropolitan"

148
00:09:15.069 --> 00:09:16.869
Penebusan?

